siriushq/stellar.lifecycle.natives.maven
========================================

Maven build plugin for generation of native classifier artifacts.

This plugin can automatically fetch from a remote source, or the local
filesystem, and caches using a hash file (SHA-* or MD5), if provided.

Per classifier name, one artifact is generated, which contains any number of
named binaries, where classifier names are platform targets.

usage
=====

Check [/src/test/resources/my-project.pom] for an example.
This demonstrates downloading and embedding the OpenCV library.

Then, see the readme of [siriushq/stellar.lifecycle.natives] for
information about how to utilize the embedded library.